OL,5, Retailers are ramping up promotions to 
OL,6, try to persuade shoppers to spend more 
OL,7, after July's wet weather hit business. 
OL,9,FSales of clothing and shoes declined   
OL,10,Flast month, which is usually a busy    
OL,11,Fmonth for fashion, as shoppers held    
OL,12,Fback from updating their summer        
OL,13,Fwardrobes.                             
OL,15,FBut a report on retail sales said there
OL,16,Fwas a "big rise" in offers designed to 
OL,17,Fpersuade shoppers back.                
OL,19,FThe higher cost of living and rising   
OL,20,Finterest rates are squeezing spending. 
